{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-template-js","path":"/projects/earth-images/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Below are a series of images I’ve taken next to the same location captured by one of our Earth observing satellites, mainly <a href=\"https://landsat.gsfc.nasa.gov/landsat-data-continuity-mission/\">Landsat-8</a> or <a href=\"https://sentinel.esa.int/web/sentinel/missions/sentinel-2\">Sentinel-2</a>. I make these for no other reason than to enjoy the difference in perspective they offer and play around with satellite imagery.</p>\n<p>In putting them together, I mainly follow the workflow laid out in this <a href=\"https://medium.com/@robsimmon/making-sense-of-satellite-data-an-open-source-workflow-accessing-data-8f7f3c30f151\">series of articles</a> written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rsimmon\">Rob Simmon</a>. It involves using <a href=\"https://www.gdal.org/\">GDAL</a>, a library for working with geospatial data, to process the raw satellite data, and <a href=\"https://www.gimp.org/\">GIMP</a>, and open-source image editing software, to further enhance the image. I then use Instagram to stick them next to an image I’ve taken.</p>\n<div class=\"imageBlock\">\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Venice, Italy\" title=\"Venice, Italy\" src=\"/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/8e1fc/earth-img-venice.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/863e1/earth-img-venice.jpg 225w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/20e5d/earth-img-venice.jpg 450w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/8e1fc/earth-img-venice.jpg 900w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/b768e/earth-img-venice.jpg 1350w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/d9c39/earth-img-venice.jpg 1800w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/e1596/earth-img-venice.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Venice, Italy</span> eft: Landsat-8 564 false color image captured 4/19/2015; Right: me 08/2015 right after I got pooped on by a pigeon.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Denali, AK\" title=\"Denali, AK\" src=\"/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/8e1fc/earth-img-denali.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/863e1/earth-img-denali.jpg 225w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/20e5d/earth-img-denali.jpg 450w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/8e1fc/earth-img-denali.jpg 900w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/b768e/earth-img-denali.jpg 1350w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/d9c39/earth-img-denali.jpg 1800w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/e1596/earth-img-denali.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Denali, AK</span> A typically cloud-covered Denali from up there and down here. Top: a very luck me on 07/23/2017 Bottom: a similarly lucky Landsat-8 on 07/22/2017.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Boston, MA\" title=\"Boston, MA\" src=\"/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/8e1fc/earth-img-boston.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/863e1/earth-img-boston.jpg 225w,\n/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/20e5d/earth-img-boston.jpg 450w,\n/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/8e1fc/earth-img-boston.jpg 900w,\n/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/b768e/earth-img-boston.jpg 1350w,\n/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/d9c39/earth-img-boston.jpg 1800w,\n/static/c84254e6f9b02a4a4db61742cd3ea2e8/e1596/earth-img-boston.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Boston, MA</span> Hometown from far from the ground and farther from the ground. Top: true color composite (432) courtesy of Landsat 8 OLI on August 30, 2016. Bottom: me from a plane.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Plumb Island, MA\" title=\"Plumb Island, MA\" src=\"/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/8e1fc/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/863e1/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg 225w,\n/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/20e5d/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg 450w,\n/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/8e1fc/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg 900w,\n/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/b768e/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg 1350w,\n/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/d9c39/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg 1800w,\n/static/a0bfbbb39f88cb30746303c0645fcc41/e1596/earth-img-plumbIsland.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Plumb Island, MA</span> OH those summer nights Top: me late summer 2017 Bottom: False color composite (652) captured by Sentinel-2 on September 27, 2017.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Leon Dormido, Ecuador\" title=\"Leon Dormido, Ecuador\" src=\"/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/8e1fc/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/863e1/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg 225w,\n/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/20e5d/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg 450w,\n/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/8e1fc/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg 900w,\n/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/b768e/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg 1350w,\n/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/d9c39/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg 1800w,\n/static/d36c3da5501e469827e810294e59dcb2/e1596/earth-img-leonDormido.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Leon Dormido, Ecuador</span> Top: Leon Dormido sitting off the coast of San Cristóbal Island, Galapagos as viewed by Landsat-8. Bottom: me from a boat.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Cape Cod, MA\" title=\"Cape Cod, MA\" src=\"/static/559d18b0216118fbb2cbf0cb380752b7/c08c5/earth-img-provincetown.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/559d18b0216118fbb2cbf0cb380752b7/863e1/earth-img-provincetown.jpg 225w,\n/static/559d18b0216118fbb2cbf0cb380752b7/20e5d/earth-img-provincetown.jpg 450w,\n/static/559d18b0216118fbb2cbf0cb380752b7/c08c5/earth-img-provincetown.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Figure 6:</span> True color composite (432). Landsat 8 OLI; October 8, 2015.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Earth Images","myRole":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/earth-images/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}